            int "Number of Mixer Sources"
            range 0 8
            default 0
            help
                Number of input sources to configure.
                Note:
                1) The actual number of mixer sources can exceed this range.
                   Users can modify the mixer configuration by calling `OBJ_GET_CFG` to get
                   the original mixer configuration structure.
                2) If set to 0, the default configuration `DEFAULT_ESP_GMF_MIXER_CONFIG` will be used.

